sections.text: audit report.A report of the findings of any energy audit conducted under the Deferred Building Renewal Act shall be sent electronically to the state agency operating or managing the state-owned building, utility, or ground on which the audit was conducted and the Committee on Building Maintenance of the Legislature.SourceLaws 2011, LB228, ยง 3.
